query:
SELECT 
  ce.id, ce.courseId, ce.feeId, ce.traineeCount, ce.paidAmount, ce.dailyStatId,
  c.name as courseName,
  cf.name as feeName, cf.amount as feeAmount
FROM courseEnrollments ce
LEFT JOIN courses c ON ce.courseId = c.id
LEFT JOIN courseFees cf ON ce.feeId = cf.id
WHERE c.name LIKE '%تصوير%'
ORDER BY ce.id DESC
LIMIT 10;
